    {
      "content": "DocumentDB supports the following Open Geospatial Consortium (OGC) built-in functions for geospatial querying.",
      "pos": [
        7464,
        7574
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "For more details on the complete set of built-in functions in the SQL language, please refer to <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt>Query DocumentDB<ept id=\"p1\">](documentdb-sql-query.md)</ept>.",
