    },
    {
      "content": "The DocumentDB .NET SDK also providers stub methods <ph id=\"ph1\">`Distance()`</ph> and <ph id=\"ph2\">`Within()`</ph> for use within LINQ expressions.",
      "pos": [
        11922,
